This is really edge case situation where APIs provide list and detail endpoints and in the endpoint which returns the list of records adds link to detail url

```json
{
  "series": {
    "items": [
      {
        "resourceURI": "http://gateway.marvel.com/v1/public/series/8",
        "name": "Call, the Vol. 2: The Precinct (2003)"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```
